            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li><code>~~v</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(v||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>inverse(inverse(v))</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(v||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>a \u2227 a</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(0||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>a + a</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(2 a||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>3(2v)</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(6 v||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>R~R</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(1||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>\u2016unit(v)\u2016</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(1||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>\u27e8v\u27e9\u2081 (v is grade-1)</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(v||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>\u27e8v\u27e9\u2082 (v is grade-1)</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(0||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>a \u2212 (\u2212a)</code> \u2192 <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(2 a||)</marimo-tex></li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
